                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-785-18600917 t18600917-785-punishment-45"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The officer Franklyn stated that the prisoners had been convicted together of an aggravated assault.</hi>
